      "name": "Class III centrifugal VAD hemolysis applicability constraint",
      "description": "Model applicability is restricted to centrifugal blood pumps operating within the FDA generic pump geometry envelope, blood viscosity 3.0–4.5 cP, hematocrit 35–45%, rotational speeds 2000–4000 RPM, and flow rates 3–8 L/min. Extrapolation beyond these bounds is not supported by the available validation evidence."
    },
    "hasOperatingEnvelope": {
